snippet.title: Ape Reunion Metaverse Attack Animations and Items Update 12/13
snippet.description:
ApeReunion is a 2d metaverse with MMORPG elements that is currently in development. Open beta is available to all holders.

Updates:
- New quick access bar
- Many new items for attacking and harvesting resources
- New animation preview
